content.rendered:
The Riseley Poseur Height Picnic table is one of our fantastic new picnic table additions. This very sturdy, easy to assemble picnic table is made from solid treated timber, giving you ease of mind that it will last for years to come.

Made with Spruce Wood and Impregnated with a high quality wood preserver.

Available in various sizes

This item is in stock for delivery in 2-4 working days.

This comes with a 1 year guarantee.
